"title": "5369: kingship, divine",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5369",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God is sovereign over all the earth. Jesus Christ is the true King of Israel and David's greater son.</p>\n<h2>The kingship of God</h2>\n<h3>God is sovereign over all the earth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:11-1Chr29:12\">1CH 29:11–29:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:18\">EXO 15:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:31\">1CH 16:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:7-Ps9:8\">PSA 9:7–9:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:6\">PSA 45:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:19\">PSA 103:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:16\">ISA 37:16</a></p>\n<h3>God is called king</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:10\">PSA 29:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps47:6-Ps47:7\">PSA 47:6–47:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:12\">1SA 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps47:2\">PSA 47:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:3\">PSA 95:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:5\">ISA 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:6\">ISA 44:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:17\">1TI 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:15\">1TI 6:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:3\">REV 15:3</a></p>\n<h3>God rules as king</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:10\">PSA 96:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps47:8\">PSA 47:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps93:1\">PSA 93:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:1\">PSA 97:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps99:1\">PSA 99:1</a></p>\n<h3>The kingdom of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:14-Mark1:15\">MRK 1:14–1:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:11-Ps145:13\">PSA 145:11–145:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:17\">MAT 4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:23\">MAT 4:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:12\">MAT 11:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:43\">LUK 4:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:20\">LUK 11:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:16\">LUK 16:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:24\">1CO 15:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:15\">REV 11:15</a></p>\n<h2>The kingship of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is the true king of Israel and of the world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:49\">JHN 1:49</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:5\">MAT 21:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:9\">ZEC 9:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:2\">MRK 15:2</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:11\">MAT 27:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:3\">LUK 23:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:36-John18:37\">JHN 18:36–18:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:7\">ACT 17:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:8\">HEB 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:6\">PSA 45:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:14\">REV 17:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:16\">REV 19:16</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is David's greater son</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:32-Luke1:33\">LUK 1:32–1:33</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:36-Acts13:37\">ACT 13:36–13:37</a></strong> <em>Jesus Christ is not only David's son but he is greater than David.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:1\">MAT 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:35-Mark12:37\">MRK 12:35–12:37</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:41-Matt22:45\">MAT 22:41–22:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:41-Luke20:44\">LUK 20:41–20:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:69\">LUK 1:69</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:29-Acts2:36\">ACT 2:29–2:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:22-Acts13:23\">ACT 13:22–13:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:3\">ROM 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:8\">2TI 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:5\">REV 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:16\">REV 22:16</a></p>\n<h2>The kingship of believers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:12\">2TI 2:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:6\">EPH 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9\">1PE 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:26-Rev2:27\">REV 2:26–2:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:21\">REV 3:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:10\">REV 5:10</a></p>",
